against Fengliu Shop.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:01:58.950
In the event of Liu Yan realizing

00:01:58.950 --> 00:02:00.020
he has been tricked,

00:02:00.020 --> 00:02:02.220
try to stall him for as long as possible.

00:02:03.070 --> 00:02:03.590
Besides,

00:02:03.590 --> 00:02:05.070
though Master Puzhu was injured before,

00:02:05.070 --> 00:02:06.280
he's about to fully recover.

00:02:06.280 --> 00:02:07.420
Perhaps we can hold out

00:02:07.420 --> 00:02:09.820
till the imperial reinforcements arrive.

00:02:11.230 --> 00:02:12.300
I see.

00:02:12.890 --> 00:02:14.870
Shao Yanping is truly a conniving man.

00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:16.930
He tricked me with a bunch of dummies.

00:02:17.340 --> 00:02:17.970
Exactly.

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:19.390
It's getting dark soon.

00:02:19.420 --> 00:02:21.170
The imperial reinforcements
could arrive anytime.

00:02:21.170 --> 00:02:22.150
I suggest you quit

00:02:22.150 --> 00:02:23.010
and go home now.

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.520
Leave before it's too late.

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.310
Or you might just

00:02:25.310 --> 00:02:27.110
lose everything in Mount Cloud.

00:02:27.710 --> 00:02:29.420
As long as I can catch Tang Lici,

00:02:29.420 --> 00:02:31.880
I don't mind losing
the entire Fengliu Shop.

00:02:32.710 --> 00:02:34.840
I bet he's still at the Sword Alliance.

00:02:36.150 --> 00:02:37.310
Stop him!

00:02:37.590 --> 00:02:38.310
Red lotus over the fire.

00:02:38.310 --> 00:02:39.510
Gone with the shadow!

00:02:50.190 --> 00:02:50.990
This medicine

00:02:51.060 --> 00:02:53.310
won't fully neutralize the fire poison,

00:02:53.310 --> 00:02:54.400
but it can ease

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:56.000
Master Puzhu's pain for now.

00:02:56.240 --> 00:02:57.770
Since you're already here,

00:02:58.000 --> 00:02:58.960
why leave?

00:02:59.950 --> 00:03:00.740
Sir,

00:03:01.470 --> 00:03:02.630
don't forget

00:03:03.960 --> 00:03:05.760
that we stand on opposite sides.

00:03:05.850 --> 00:03:06.910
If that's the case,

00:03:07.730 --> 00:03:08.360
why

00:03:08.910 --> 00:03:09.750
save me at all?

00:03:10.670 --> 00:03:11.800
I'm indebted to you.

00:03:12.610 --> 00:03:14.340
I wanted to offer myself to you,

00:03:14.910 --> 00:03:16.370
but I feared you'd refuse,

00:03:16.590 --> 00:03:18.650
so all I could give was this antidote.

00:03:32.850 --> 00:03:34.180
What are you doing here?

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:36.340
Sir, it took you 7 days to heal.

00:03:36.540 --> 00:03:37.820
I figured

00:03:37.840 --> 00:03:39.190
that you'd definitely return

00:03:39.190 --> 00:03:40.670
to the battlefield after you recovered.

00:03:40.670 --> 00:03:42.070
So, I decided to wait here

00:03:42.350 --> 00:03:43.700
for you, Master Puzhu.

00:03:44.530 --> 00:03:45.740
Why risk coming here?

00:03:47.310 --> 00:03:48.120
To visit you.

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:50.750
To assassinate you.

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:53.870
Master Puzhu,

00:03:54.490 --> 00:03:55.890
which answer do you like?

00:03:56.430 --> 00:03:57.840
I like you...

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:01.170
forsaking the wrong for the right.

00:04:02.790 --> 00:04:04.030
"Like"?

00:04:07.190 --> 00:04:08.520
By that, I meant I hoped.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:17.510
That's not strong enough.

00:04:18.980 --> 00:04:20.620
I want you to like me.

00:04:24.820 --> 00:04:26.190
Liu Yan has gone crazy.

00:04:26.750 --> 00:04:29.280
Fengliu Shop will absolutely fall
tomorrow.

00:04:30.390 --> 00:04:32.590
About the Nine Qilin Transformations,

00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:34.110
I can tell you a secret.

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:45.960
Does this count as

00:04:46.630 --> 00:04:49.560
"forsaking the wrong for the right"
—which you like?

00:04:54.990 --> 00:04:56.770
[Tingyun Pavilion]

00:05:13.040 --> 00:05:14.280
Do you know

00:05:14.600 --> 00:05:16.000
who killed your brother?

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:19.680
It was Tang Lici.

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:23.370
Shei.

00:05:24.270 --> 00:05:25.050
You're here.

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:27.430
Miss Shei,

00:05:28.550 --> 00:05:29.810
why didn't you come in?

00:05:42.670 --> 00:05:44.110
He looks peaceful.

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:45.750
Is he recovering?

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.050
No, he's dying.

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:05.170
The poison in him is quite unusual.

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:07.310
It seems to have been made
particularly for him.

00:06:07.310 --> 00:06:09.110
There's nothing I can do to help.

00:06:09.430 --> 00:06:10.390
To add to that,

00:06:10.590 --> 00:06:12.390
the heart crystal in his abdomen

00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:15.510
is slowly killing him.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:16.720
Heart crystal?

00:06:17.750 --> 00:06:18.880
What heart crystal?

00:06:19.660 --> 00:06:21.120
You don't know about that?

00:06:23.190 --> 00:06:24.160
In his abdomen

00:06:24.960 --> 00:06:26.960
resides Fang Zhou's heart crystal.

00:06:34.650 --> 00:06:35.580
Whose is it?

00:06:37.510 --> 00:06:38.970
Whose heart crystal is it?

00:06:39.190 --> 00:06:40.070
Fang Zhou's.

00:06:44.110 --> 00:06:44.750
Senior!

00:06:45.770 --> 00:06:46.700
Is there a chance

00:06:47.230 --> 00:06:48.820
for Fang Zhou to be revived?

00:06:49.710 --> 00:06:51.030
His body has vanished.

00:06:51.090 --> 00:06:52.290
How can he be revived?

00:06:56.310 --> 00:06:57.050
Besides,

00:06:57.350 --> 00:06:59.550
if his heart crystal is to be preserved,

00:07:02.000 --> 00:07:03.720
Tang Lici will die.

00:07:30.980 --> 00:07:32.440
There's only one cure now.

00:07:32.909 --> 00:07:34.600
That is, when Tang Lici wakes up,

00:07:34.600 --> 00:07:36.600
he'll have to use his Rebirth Scroll

00:07:36.870 --> 00:07:38.330
to transfer all the toxins

00:07:38.630 --> 00:07:40.290
to Fang Zhou's heart crystal.

00:07:40.550 --> 00:07:42.280
Only in that way can he survive.

00:07:52.500 --> 00:07:53.570
What if

00:07:57.600 --> 00:07:58.830
he can't wake up?

00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:02.240
Then he'll die in a beautiful dream

00:08:02.630 --> 00:08:04.480
with that heart crystal.

00:08:11.050 --> 00:08:11.850
And what if

00:08:15.160 --> 00:08:16.270
he wakes up?

00:08:16.950 --> 00:08:18.220
When that happens,

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.400
he'll surely regret

00:08:19.820 --> 00:08:21.730
not dying in the dream.

00:08:23.210 --> 00:08:23.740
That way,

00:08:24.160 --> 00:08:24.750
at least

00:08:24.750 --> 00:08:26.750
he won't have to make a tough choice.

00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.120
This is...

00:09:02.870 --> 00:09:04.240
Zhoudi Tower?

00:09:06.400 --> 00:09:07.920
Why am I here?

00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:10.240
No.

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:11.640
No!

00:09:12.860 --> 00:09:15.390
Don't go away, Fang Zhou...

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:17.410
Right.

00:09:18.150 --> 00:09:19.610
Fang Zhou is forever gone.

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:22.030
His things remain,

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:23.890
yet he no longer exists.

00:09:24.630 --> 00:09:25.390
Fang Zhou,

00:09:26.300 --> 00:09:26.970
I'm sorry.

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:28.680
I'm useless.

00:09:29.750 --> 00:09:31.240
I couldn't bring you back.

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:33.000
Lici.

00:09:37.320 --> 00:09:38.580
Are you looking for me?

00:09:48.320 --> 00:09:49.000
Senior...

00:09:55.400 --> 00:09:56.800
I thought you already...

00:10:03.350 --> 00:10:04.280
It really is you.

00:10:12.190 --> 00:10:12.830
Lici,

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:14.600
did you have a bad dream?

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:16.840
There, there.

00:10:17.120 --> 00:10:17.780
All is fine.

00:10:18.060 --> 00:10:19.510
Dreams are the opposite of reality.

00:10:19.510 --> 00:10:21.370
The good thing is you've woken up.

00:10:21.750 --> 00:10:23.270
Today is your birthday.

00:10:23.660 --> 00:10:25.260
Everyone is waiting for you.

00:10:43.790 --> 00:10:44.990
Why just stand there?

00:10:45.850 --> 00:10:46.580
Come and eat.

00:10:50.550 --> 00:10:51.480
Little Monster,

00:10:51.670 --> 00:10:52.930
what's with your eyes?

00:10:53.390 --> 00:10:54.650
Why do you look so pale?

00:10:55.360 --> 00:10:57.220
Did you not sleep well last night?

00:10:58.270 --> 00:10:59.120
I'm fine.

00:10:59.290 --> 00:11:00.770
I just had a dream.

00:11:03.200 --> 00:11:04.000
A bad dream.

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:05.850
It must've been a bad dream.

00:11:07.080 --> 00:11:07.750
It's alright now.

00:11:07.750 --> 00:11:08.870
That was in the past.

00:11:08.870 --> 00:11:09.870
Come on, sit down.

00:11:11.910 --> 00:11:13.120
A mere bad dream, wasn't it?

00:11:13.120 --> 00:11:13.920
Let's eat now.

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:15.510
How about we play a tune together

00:11:15.510 --> 00:11:16.270
to soothe

00:11:16.670 --> 00:11:17.940
Little Monster's nerves later?

00:11:17.940 --> 00:11:18.690
Sounds good.

00:11:18.710 --> 00:11:20.570
We'll play the piece composed by Senior—

00:11:20.570 --> 00:11:22.430
"Wishing Each Other a Long Life."

00:11:29.550 --> 00:11:30.550
How wonderful.

00:11:31.150 --> 00:11:32.420
You're all here.

00:11:35.920 --> 00:11:37.250
I've finally come back.

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:41.580
As it turns out,

00:11:43.150 --> 00:11:44.150
all that happened

00:11:45.530 --> 00:11:46.770
was just a bad dream.

00:11:47.680 --> 00:11:49.080
What did you dream about?

00:11:49.670 --> 00:11:51.330
I dreamed that 10 years later,

00:11:52.230 --> 00:11:53.960
Yique Yinyang made a comeback,

00:11:55.430 --> 00:11:56.400
yet you, Senior,

00:11:57.810 --> 00:11:59.210
were not around anymore.

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:02.750
Those...

00:12:03.950 --> 00:12:05.270
who died trying to stop

00:12:05.290 --> 00:12:06.330
Yique Yinyang

00:12:07.320 --> 00:12:08.520
were never to return.

00:12:10.320 --> 00:12:11.580
All the sacrifices...

00:12:13.810 --> 00:12:14.900
were in vain.

00:12:16.630 --> 00:12:17.550
Lici,

00:12:17.850 --> 00:12:19.780
just think about how many children

00:12:19.860 --> 00:12:21.550
would grow up safely and healthily,

00:12:21.550 --> 00:12:23.600
and how many family
would be spared from separation

00:12:23.600 --> 00:12:24.800
during these 10 years

00:12:25.750 --> 00:12:26.830
of peace.

00:12:27.320 --> 00:12:29.380
Spring comes again after snow melts.

00:12:29.390 --> 00:12:30.190
In this world,

00:12:30.960 --> 00:12:32.760
not a second of effort is wasted.

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:34.030
Although sometimes

00:12:34.030 --> 00:12:35.290
hope may be shattered,

00:12:36.050 --> 00:12:37.370
new hope

00:12:37.720 --> 00:12:38.790
would always rise

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.420
from destruction.

00:12:51.960 --> 00:12:53.320
New hope?

00:12:54.120 --> 00:12:55.270
New hope

00:12:55.270 --> 00:12:56.070
and new people

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:57.840
are right with you.

00:13:05.790 --> 00:13:06.390
But you are

00:13:06.390 --> 00:13:07.720
already with me now.

00:13:08.060 --> 00:13:09.260
There are others too.

00:13:23.630 --> 00:13:25.080
What are they doing here?

00:13:27.500 --> 00:13:29.300
These people come from my dream.

00:13:36.770 --> 00:13:38.300
They're here to pick you up.

00:13:41.430 --> 00:13:42.640
They need you back.

00:13:43.670 --> 00:13:44.470
New hope

00:13:44.590 --> 00:13:46.320
lies in these friends of yours.

00:14:01.890 --> 00:14:02.650
Miss Shui,

00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:04.560
how is Mr. Tang's condition?

00:14:15.910 --> 00:14:17.540
So, that was not a bad dream.

00:14:26.610 --> 00:14:26.960
I couldn't save you.

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:29.390
♪ Echoes sink in silent surges ♪

00:14:29.390 --> 00:14:29.820
I still failed to save your life
in the end.

00:14:29.820 --> 00:14:32.030
♪ Surpassing many words ♪

00:14:32.030 --> 00:14:32.960
That said, Lici,

00:14:33.670 --> 00:14:33.880
you already did a lot of things

00:14:33.880 --> 00:14:36.030
♪ On the way back, a half-lit oil lamp ♪

00:14:36.030 --> 00:14:36.630
and rescued many lives.

00:14:36.630 --> 00:14:39.150
♪ Wet ink stains surge and overflow ♪

00:14:39.150 --> 00:14:40.060
Though you couldn't revive me,

00:14:40.060 --> 00:14:40.910
♪ Hope what's hopeful,
and let go of anger in a day ♪

00:14:40.910 --> 00:14:41.870
