00:14:41.870 --> 00:14:43.240
countless lives in my stead.

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:44.200
That was all I ever wanted—

00:14:44.200 --> 00:14:45.660
the continuation of life.

00:14:46.820 --> 00:14:47.630
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
live up to it, and never let you go ♪

00:14:47.630 --> 00:14:49.160
Do you remember the meaning

00:14:49.200 --> 00:14:50.080
of your name?

00:14:51.240 --> 00:14:52.840
One of a kind in a millennium,

00:14:52.870 --> 00:14:54.120
break with old words.

00:14:54.440 --> 00:14:54.630
♪ Listen to the rain ♪

00:14:54.630 --> 00:14:55.750
Then let's call you

00:14:56.360 --> 00:14:57.120
Tang Lici.

00:14:57.120 --> 00:15:00.340
♪ Whispering nonstop in my ears ♪

00:15:01.020 --> 00:15:01.870
♪ Wake, the cloud in dreams ♪

00:15:01.870 --> 00:15:03.730
I found you at the foot of Mount Li.

00:15:03.890 --> 00:15:05.120
♪ Can't hide the stars in my eyes ♪

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:06.120
I hoped

00:15:06.550 --> 00:15:07.280
you could live a different life

00:15:07.280 --> 00:15:08.030
♪ Broken promises made ♪

00:15:08.030 --> 00:15:09.100
from the one you had had.

00:15:09.100 --> 00:15:11.290
♪ Burning fire ♪

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:13.780
♪ The merciful Buddha ♪

00:15:13.800 --> 00:15:16.600
♪ All are seen through ♪

00:15:16.630 --> 00:15:16.750
♪ Shine even as I fall ♪

00:15:16.750 --> 00:15:17.750
This child

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:19.030
actually has

00:15:19.030 --> 00:15:21.290
the same constitution as Yique Yinyang.

00:15:22.000 --> 00:15:24.260
If he directs his power
to good causes...

00:15:28.060 --> 00:15:28.870
Lici,

00:15:28.900 --> 00:15:31.140
Shenzhou is not Tianren Realm.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.750
Your golden eyes and forehead mark

00:15:33.750 --> 00:15:35.150
can't define who you are.

00:15:35.160 --> 00:15:36.600
-Issue a warrant for Tang Lici!
-Issue a warrant for Tang Lici!

00:15:36.600 --> 00:15:38.790
-Kill Yique Yinyang!
-Kill Yique Yinyang!

00:15:38.790 --> 00:15:40.270
-Issue a warrant for Tang Lici!
-Issue a warrant for Tang Lici!

00:15:40.270 --> 00:15:41.510
-Kill Yique Yinyang!
-Kill Yique Yinyang!

00:15:41.510 --> 00:15:42.570
♪ On the endless cold night ♪

00:15:42.570 --> 00:15:43.360
Sir, you saw

00:15:43.390 --> 00:15:44.380
my golden eyes and forehead mark,

00:15:44.380 --> 00:15:45.170
♪ Strange is but the crescent moon ♪

00:15:45.170 --> 00:15:46.130
yet instead of killing me,

00:15:46.130 --> 00:15:47.590
you saved me instead. Why?

00:15:47.750 --> 00:15:48.140
It's better to wrongly condemn

00:15:48.140 --> 00:15:49.670
♪ The flute fades far away ♪

00:15:49.670 --> 00:15:50.930
those related to Yique Yinyang
than to let them go.

00:15:50.930 --> 00:15:52.480
♪ What's familiar will also change ♪

00:15:52.480 --> 00:15:53.720
Besides,

00:15:54.080 --> 00:15:54.990
I think your golden eyes and forehead mark

00:15:54.990 --> 00:15:56.550
♪ Ice melts in palms ♪

00:15:56.550 --> 00:15:57.600
look pretty nice.

00:15:57.900 --> 00:15:58.910
♪ Hands warm a soul ♪

00:15:58.910 --> 00:16:00.750
What shapes you is your thought

00:16:01.240 --> 00:16:01.450
and beliefs.

00:16:01.450 --> 00:16:03.440
♪ Dream of you once,
and miss you 10,000 times ♪

00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:03.790
Zhoudi Tower
is the starting point for you,

00:16:03.790 --> 00:16:06.170
♪ Spring sounds break,
and dreams never wake ♪

00:16:06.170 --> 00:16:07.370
not the destination.

00:16:08.080 --> 00:16:08.550
During your journey in Shenzhou,

00:16:08.550 --> 00:16:10.000
♪ Echoes sink in silent surges ♪

00:16:10.000 --> 00:16:11.130
you made new friends

00:16:11.390 --> 00:16:11.400
and understood love.

00:16:11.400 --> 00:16:12.150
♪ Surpassing many words ♪

00:16:12.150 --> 00:16:13.000
Plus,

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:15.460
many people need you now.

00:16:15.460 --> 00:16:16.750
♪ On the way back, a half-lit oil lamp ♪

00:16:16.750 --> 00:16:17.550
Go back.

00:16:18.080 --> 00:16:18.210
The capable, more than others,
should bring benefits to all people.

00:16:18.210 --> 00:16:21.450
♪ Wet ink stains surge and overflow ♪

00:16:21.550 --> 00:16:21.640
Live with a clear conscience.

00:16:21.640 --> 00:16:23.320
♪ Hope what's hopeful,
and let go of anger in a day ♪

00:16:23.320 --> 00:16:25.250
Don't complain even in adversity.

00:16:28.400 --> 00:16:31.670
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
live up to it, and never let you go ♪

00:16:31.670 --> 00:16:33.240
I can't stay here.

00:16:36.020 --> 00:16:38.410
♪ Listen to the rain ♪

00:16:38.700 --> 00:16:40.440
♪ Whispering nonstop in my ears ♪

00:16:40.440 --> 00:16:41.270
Fang Zhou...

00:16:42.600 --> 00:16:43.630
♪ Wake, the cloud in dreams ♪

00:16:43.630 --> 00:16:44.670
I get it now.

00:16:45.470 --> 00:16:48.830
♪ Can't hide the stars in my eyes ♪

00:16:48.860 --> 00:16:50.640
♪ Broken promises made ♪

00:16:50.660 --> 00:16:52.880
♪ Burning fire ♪

00:16:52.900 --> 00:16:55.360
♪ The merciful Buddha ♪

00:16:55.380 --> 00:16:55.870
♪ All are seen through ♪

