00:35:12.550 --> 00:35:13.550
once merged the century-old

00:35:13.550 --> 00:35:15.010
pure energy in Mount Cloud

00:35:15.630 --> 00:35:17.560
with the energy in Tianyang Sword,

00:35:18.150 --> 00:35:19.950
and stored it in the dragon head.

00:35:20.230 --> 00:35:21.590
As soon as we activate it,

00:35:21.590 --> 00:35:23.360
a massive formation of sword energy
will emerge

00:35:23.360 --> 00:35:25.710
and blow up
the Nine Qilin Transformations.

00:35:25.710 --> 00:35:28.640
I am a direct disciple
of Zhao Quanyang the Ancestor.

00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:31.170
I can be a sacrificial offering

00:35:32.110 --> 00:35:33.150
for the sword!

00:35:33.670 --> 00:35:34.520
Don't, Sword Master!

00:35:34.520 --> 00:35:36.320
You can't do that, Sword Master!

00:35:36.710 --> 00:35:39.590
♪ You're already here, so don't go ♪

00:35:39.610 --> 00:35:42.520
♪ So what if you go? ♪

00:35:42.550 --> 00:35:45.370
♪ I talked to the rain last night ♪

00:35:45.910 --> 00:35:48.620
♪ The flowers have bloomed ♪

00:35:48.640 --> 00:35:49.510
♪ You're already here, so don't go ♪

00:35:49.510 --> 00:35:50.590
Although sometimes

00:35:50.590 --> 00:35:51.690
hope may be shattered,

00:35:51.690 --> 00:35:52.590
♪ If you go, don't look back ♪

00:35:52.590 --> 00:35:53.630
new hope

00:35:54.880 --> 00:35:54.970
would always

00:35:54.970 --> 00:35:56.510
♪ No need to stay ♪

00:35:56.510 --> 00:35:57.840
rise from destruction.

00:35:58.180 --> 00:36:00.850
♪ Just go alone ♪

00:36:01.190 --> 00:36:04.180
♪ In the mortal world ♪

00:36:04.190 --> 00:36:04.410
The Six Scriptures of Justice—

00:36:04.410 --> 00:36:06.030
♪ There are too many dreams ♪

00:36:06.030 --> 00:36:07.170
mighty winds and thunders,
revolutionize the world!

00:36:07.170 --> 00:36:10.430
♪ In mountains and rivers ♪

00:36:10.450 --> 00:36:16.200
♪ There are too many dreams ♪

00:36:16.640 --> 00:36:18.190
♪ From now on ♪

00:36:18.210 --> 00:36:21.160
♪ Bone wastes, mortal dust,
instant world ♪

00:36:21.180 --> 00:36:23.180
♪ All blend into one flow ♪

00:36:23.470 --> 00:36:28.840
♪ Burn this life to embers,
and I have no one to rest with ♪

00:36:28.950 --> 00:36:29.960
♪ From now on ♪

00:36:29.960 --> 00:36:30.580
Tang Lici,

00:36:30.580 --> 00:36:31.760
♪ My scars and my pure loyalty ♪

00:36:31.760 --> 00:36:33.420
the Thousand Curse Needle
has gone deep into your system.

00:36:33.420 --> 00:36:34.110
♪ I'll never return them in this life ♪

00:36:34.110 --> 00:36:35.280
You're launching the last strike

00:36:35.280 --> 00:36:35.760
of your life.

00:36:35.760 --> 00:36:37.000
♪ I can't stand
hearing other people's happiness ♪

00:36:37.000 --> 00:36:37.590
What?

00:36:41.160 --> 00:36:42.790
♪ From now on ♪

00:36:42.820 --> 00:36:43.960
♪ Under the sword,
my old friends and I get drunk ♪

00:36:43.960 --> 00:36:44.550
Retreat!

00:36:44.760 --> 00:36:45.360
Retreat!

00:36:45.710 --> 00:36:47.800
♪ Let's talk about life and death
when we wake up ♪

00:36:48.010 --> 00:36:53.290
♪ Only leave a broken chessboard behind ♪

00:36:53.560 --> 00:36:53.880
♪ From now on ♪

00:36:53.880 --> 00:36:54.610
Fang Zhou...

00:36:55.250 --> 00:36:55.510
♪ The vast land stretches before my eyes ♪

00:36:55.510 --> 00:36:56.430
I made it.

00:36:58.220 --> 00:37:00.220
♪ Don't be alone ♪

00:37:00.670 --> 00:37:06.810
♪ And only left torn joy and sorrow
on the ground ♪

00:37:21.520 --> 00:37:22.520
Master!

00:37:32.030 --> 00:37:32.830
Sword Master,

00:37:33.100 --> 00:37:34.250
the imperial forces
and those from Biluo Palace

00:37:34.250 --> 00:37:34.850
have arrived.

00:37:34.850 --> 00:37:35.840
Violence has subsided everywhere,

00:37:35.840 --> 00:37:37.290
except in the southern mountainside.

00:37:37.290 --> 00:37:38.000
Great!

00:37:38.710 --> 00:37:40.030
Puzhu is guarding

00:37:40.770 --> 00:37:42.370
the southern mountainside.

00:37:49.880 --> 00:37:50.810
My masterpiece!

00:37:50.920 --> 00:37:51.760
My creation!

00:37:52.660 --> 00:37:54.630
Look what you've all done!

00:37:56.320 --> 00:37:57.100
Puzhu!

00:37:57.710 --> 00:37:58.680
There's one more trick up my sleeve.

00:37:58.680 --> 00:38:00.810
You'll pay for my works with your life!

00:38:06.120 --> 00:38:07.850
What are you doing, Xifang Tao?

00:38:17.710 --> 00:38:18.480
Sir, if you agree

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:20.230
to keep me safe at the Sword Alliance,

00:38:20.230 --> 00:38:21.960
I'll forsake the wrong for the right

00:38:21.960 --> 00:38:23.480
and help you eliminate Qiaoyi Qiankun

00:38:23.480 --> 00:38:25.680
before the Nine Qilin Transformations

00:38:25.900 --> 00:38:28.030
are repaired by the Sky-Fallen Stone.

00:38:28.550 --> 00:38:29.360
Xifang Tao,

00:38:29.550 --> 00:38:31.950
I'll drag you two to hell with me!

00:38:53.930 --> 00:38:54.760
Xifang Tao...

00:38:55.070 --> 00:38:55.800
Everyone

00:38:56.760 --> 00:38:58.320
deserves a second chance.

00:39:20.900 --> 00:39:22.250
I've transferred the Thousand Curse Needle

00:39:22.250 --> 00:39:23.410
and the toxins

00:39:24.000 --> 00:39:25.510
to this heart crystal.

00:39:26.880 --> 00:39:27.810
My dear brother,

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:31.400
should I hate him or not?

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:34.760
You love and hate him at the same time.

00:39:34.760 --> 00:39:36.230
Is that tearing you apart?

00:39:59.710 --> 00:40:02.240
This is
where Zhao Quanyang was enlightened.

00:40:02.280 --> 00:40:04.360
It's indeed a beautiful place

00:40:04.360 --> 00:40:05.510
to bury the dead.

00:40:43.510 --> 00:40:44.150
Lici,

00:40:45.150 --> 00:40:47.210
you've really become an invalid now.

00:40:55.240 --> 00:40:56.510
Why are you so quiet?

00:40:59.000 --> 00:41:00.110
Where is the eloquence

00:41:00.110 --> 00:41:01.320
you were so proud of?

00:41:01.880 --> 00:41:02.960
Where are your wit

00:41:02.960 --> 00:41:04.710
and excellent martial skills?

00:41:07.020 --> 00:41:09.060
Look at yourself now.

00:41:09.400 --> 00:41:11.110
You can't speak or move.

00:41:12.440 --> 00:41:14.110
You're just sitting there

00:41:14.110 --> 00:41:15.370
like a complete loser.

00:41:21.440 --> 00:41:22.520
What a shame

00:41:22.840 --> 00:41:24.970
that there isn't a mirror in this dump.

00:41:25.300 --> 00:41:27.740
If there was, I'd definitely make you see

00:41:27.770 --> 00:41:29.640
what you've become.

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:47.150
Do not

00:41:47.440 --> 00:41:48.110
approach

00:41:48.240 --> 00:41:48.950
my master.

00:41:49.290 --> 00:41:50.560
You call him Master?

00:41:51.110 --> 00:41:52.760
He is steeped in evil.

00:41:52.960 --> 00:41:54.190
He disowned his close ones

00:41:54.190 --> 00:41:55.600
and betrayed his master and sect.

00:41:55.600 --> 00:41:57.580
How does he deserve to be called Master?

00:41:57.580 --> 00:41:58.390
Nonsense!

00:42:25.410 --> 00:42:26.150
Don't you dare...

00:42:26.150 --> 00:42:27.110
hurt...

00:42:27.550 --> 00:42:28.630
my master...

00:42:30.920 --> 00:42:33.070
Don't kill my master...